<CAPTION>  Photos (3); PHOTO: Joe Cavaretta -- Mercury News; PROTESTERS -- Stanford
students, left, pass by demonstrators pretending they are dead soldiers.
PHOTO: Above, David Montano sleeps outside San Jose Federal Building. His
father and brother are serving in the gulf.; PHOTO: Paul Kitagaki Jr. --
Mercury News; PALESTINIAN PROTESTER-- Mona Kayyali waves a Palestinian flag
