of <LOCATION>Elmwood Park</LOCATION>, <LOCATION>N.J.</LOCATION>, and <PERSON>Lesley Lehane</PERSON> of <LOCATION>Chestnut Hill</LOCATION>, <LOCATION>Mass.</LOCATION>;
REGISTRATION: Open registration will be conducted <DATE>Friday</DATE> (between <TIME>11:30 a.m.</TIME>
and <TIME>7 p.m.</TIME>) and <DATE>Saturday</DATE> (10 a.m. to <TIME>6 p.m.</TIME>) at the Health and <ORGANIZATION>Fitness Expo</ORGANIZATION> at
the <LOCATION>Hyatt Regency</LOCATION> in <LOCATION>San Francisco</LOCATION>. Registration costs <MONEY>$45</MONEY>. No registration
will be allowed the day of the race. For more information, call (415)
896-0587.; PRIZE MONEY: <MONEY>$100,000</MONEY>. First-place finishers receive a
<ORGANIZATION>Mercedes-Benz</ORGANIZATION> 190E sedan.; TELEVISION: Channel 7 will broadcast the race from
<TIME>7:30-11 a.m.</TIME>; RADIO: KGO (810) will broadcast the race from 7 a.m.-noon.;
VIEWING INFORMATION: Anyone is allowed to line up along the course and watch
the runners.  </TEXT>
